                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2024-05-08T10:07:31.252-04:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    jcr:title="Accountability is key"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                                    type="h2"
                                    variant="h"/>
                                <text_1669197365_copy_1188738063
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                                    jcr:created="{Date}2023-05-04T01:03:19.177-04:00"
                                    jcr:createdBy="SCHAFSM"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-05-04T01:05:57.210-04:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="SCHAFSM"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>At AbbVie, employees are often reminded that accountability is key to the cultural success of the company. AbbVie employees are the driving force in amplifying the culture -- what employees do every day impacts the company’s culture.&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>Held equally accountable, AbbVie Way Ambassadors continue to work diligently to help steer the course, provide support, and ultimately ensure culture remains a top priority across the organization.&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>“AbbVie culture, as I perceive it, is multifaceted, ambitious, innovative, curious, fresh, playful, brave, and thus – human,” Schwyn says. “Culture at AbbVie does not just happen; it has been deliberately designed and has become an integral and exciting part of our daily lives.”&lt;/p>&#xa;"
                                    textIsRich="true"/>
